<sect1 id="FAQBACKU"><title>10.6. Backup</title>
<variablelist>
<listitem>
<para></para>
</listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term>Q: <para><link linkend="MMKM">Mondo says,
'Cannot run mindi --makemountlist' and aborts. What do I
do?</link></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q: <para><ulink url="faqbackup.html#AEN748">Can
