<varlistentry><term>Q:
<para><ulink url="faqbackup.html#AEN753">When I try to backup to
CD, cdrecord/mkisofs returns an error. Nothing else appears to be
wrong. What do I do?</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q:
<para><ulink url="faqbackup.html#AEN758">Mondo failed to burn my
CD. It said something like, "Error CDB A1 01 02 53 ..." and so on.
What does that mean?</ulink></para></term>
