do?</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q: <para><ulink url="faqbackup.html#AEN790">Can
Mondo backup to data files on another partition, e.g. an NFS
mount?</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q: <para><ulink url="faqbackup.html#AEN795">Can
Mondo backup _to_ an NFS partition, i.e. backup over a network? How
