<varlistentry><term>Q:
<para><ulink url="faqbackup.html#AEN801">Does Mondo handle System
or Hidden attributes when archiving Dos/Win
files?</ulink></para></term>
<varlistentry><term>Q: <para><ulink url="faqbackup.html#AEN806">Why
do you include IO.SYS and MSDOS.SYS in mondo-vfat, when they belong
